### 1. List all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks

### 2. Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Build CRUD API"
}

### 3. Get single task (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/1

### 4. Get single task (Not Found)
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/999

### 5. Update a task (Full Update)
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Master TypeScript",
  "completed": true
}

### 6. Delete a task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/2

### 7. Delete non-existent task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/999
